Distribution and habitat : Known from Southeastern and Southern Brazil (
Fig. 8
). Spiders of this genus can be found under rocks and fallen trunks in high altitudes of the Atlantic forest ( 900–2000m ), as well as in lowlands ( 0–900m ) in the countryside and coastal region of the states of Rio de Janeiro, São Paulo, Paraná and Rio Grande do Sul (
Fig. 8
).
